{"title":"开山歌","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新茶山，在何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见茶山见云雾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雾散，红日出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光闪闪照银锄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银锄落，二锤舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开辟茶园大改土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改土号子齐声吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱石荆棘排队走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山战歌齐声唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒坡野岭翻新样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新土一级垒一级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"级级连成上天梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新土一层叠一层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层向上高入云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在山头望大寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心随目光飞天外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨虽隔万里远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装在心中映在眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼下困难算个啥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水落处定开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶苗总会长成林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦创业炼新人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新人一代接一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排云拨雾紧跟来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝起新茶莫嫌苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你永作开山斧！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}